      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can barely close my eyes. im already taking some melatonin every night but it isnt really doing much. my doctor gave me some ambien (zolpidem) for when i really cant sleep so i was thinking of maybe taking both at the same time tonight so it actually works? is that cool or will it be too much?",
